data.description: Spacious East Texas Ranchette! 4 Bedroom, 3 Bath Ranch-Style Home sitting on approximately 1.7 Acres. Additional features include 2 Living Areas, WBFP, Convenient Kitchen, 4-Seasons Room. 4th Bedroom has ensuite making it a great M-I-L Suite. Huge Laundry Room. 2-Car Attached Carport. Acreage is mostly open pasture with a few scattered trees.
